summary: An ordinance accepting a deed, dated January 18, 1912, from the Seattle Heights Improvement Company, to the City of Seattle, a municipal corporation, to the "North half of the Southwest quarter of section 20, township 27 north, range 4 east, W.M., and blocks numbered 1 and 2, division 4, of the plat of Seattle Heights, containing 100 acres, more or less", situated in the County of Snohomish, State of Washington.
